<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Method "send()" (in Zend_Feed_Rss and Zend_Feed_Atom) outputs HTTP-headers in format:
{{Content-type: application/rss+xml; charset: UTF-8}}</p>

<p>but must be in format:
{{Content-Type: application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8}}
(note: upper-case letter "T" and "=" without spaces).</p>

<p>See 
1. <a href="http://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec14.html#sec14.17">http://w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/…</a> (Content-Type header description)
2. <a href="http://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec3.html#sec3.7">http://w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/…</a>  (media-type description)</p>

